    <description>Card game for 2+ players.&amp;#10;Each player controls a squadron of Privateers. &amp;#10;The object of the game is to successfully lead your pilots on missions vs pirate gangs, enemy militias, and commercial zeppelins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;VICTORY Conditions&amp;#10;The player with the most VP (Victory Points) at the end of the game wins.&amp;#10;The game ends when a player goes to draw a card and there are no cards left in the deck.&amp;#10;VP are gained by completing missions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players share a common deck. That deck contains 6 types of cards: H = Pilots, P = Planes, W = Weapons, M=Maneuvers,&amp;#10;D = Damage, V = Missions&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game also uses two six sided dice &amp;#10;Counters are used to mark damage to the planes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player is dealt 7 cards. &amp;#10;Roll high on 1D6 to see who goes first.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On ones turn the player goes through 6 phases;&amp;#10;Luck Phase&amp;#10;Recruit Phase&amp;#10;Mission Phase&amp;#10;Defender Phase&amp;#10;Action Phase&amp;#10;End Phase&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Completing misions scores points Whoever at the end of the game has completed the most missions or who has destroyed aircraft who are attempting to complete a mission is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
